title: Texas mother shoots and kills two little girls, police say
itunes:title: Texas mother shoots and kills two little girls, police say
description:
Hear the heart wrenching 911 call made by a dad who's letting police know his two little girls have been shot. Nancy Grace delves into who did it and why.
